L. Barbee Ponder IV
Executive Compensation
As General Counsel and Vice President of Regulatory Affairs at GLOBALSTAR, INC., L. Barbee Ponder IV made $1,685,882 in total compensation.  Of this total $223,907 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,457,300 was awarded as stock and $4,675 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


